{"_path":"/blog/arena-de-pellets-vs-arena-tradicional-vs-tofu","_dir":"blog","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"Arena de pellets vs. arena tradicional vs. arena de tofu: comparativa completa 2026","description":"Comparamos los tres tipos de arena para gatos disponibles en Ecuador: pellets de madera, bentonita tradicional y tofu. Rendimiento, olores, polvo, precio y impacto ambiental.","date":"2026-07-21","keywords":["arena de pellets vs arena tradicional","arena de tofu para gatos","tipos de arena para gatos","mejor arena para gatos ecuador","comparativa arenas para gatos"],"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Elegir la arena correcta es una de las decisiones que más impacto tiene en la higiene del hogar, la salud de su gato y su presupuesto mensual. En el mercado ecuatoriano conviven hoy tres grandes tipos: la "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"arena tradicional de bentonita"}]},{"type":"text","value":", la "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"arena de tofu o soya"}]},{"type":"text","value":" y la "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"arena de pellets de madera"}]},{"type":"text","value":". Las comparamos punto por punto."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"los-tres-contendientes"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Los tres contendientes"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Arena de bentonita (tradicional)."}]},{"type":"text","value":" Arcilla que forma grumos al contacto con la humedad. Es la más antigua y conocida, generalmente importada."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Arena de tofu/soya."}]},{"type":"text","value":" Fabricada con residuos de soya prensados en cilindros finos. Soluble en agua y biodegradable, popular en Asia y de llegada reciente a Latinoamérica, casi siempre importada."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Arena de pellets de madera."}]},{"type":"text","value":" Aserrín prensado a alta densidad en cilindros de 6 mm. Absorbe la orina, se deshace en aserrín y neutraliza el olor con la resina natural de la madera. En Ecuador se produce localmente."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"comparativa-punto-por-punto"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Comparativa punto por punto"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"table","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"thead","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Criterio"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Pellets de madera"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Bentonita"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"th","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Tofu / soya"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tbody","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Rendimiento"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Hasta 3 veces mayor"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Estándar"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Estándar"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Polvo"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ninguno"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Alto"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Bajo"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Control de olores"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Natural (resina)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Variable, suele usar perfumes"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Bueno"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Biodegradable"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sí, compostable"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"No"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sí"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Químicos/aditivos"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ninguno"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Frecuentes"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Variables"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Riesgo si se ingiere"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Bajo"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Medio (obstrucción)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Bajo"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Producción nacional"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Sí"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"No"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"No"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"tr","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Costo por semana de uso"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Bajo"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Alto"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"td","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Alto"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"análisis-donde-cada-arena-gana-y-pierde"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Análisis: donde cada arena gana y pierde"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"control-de-olores"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Control de olores"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"La bentonita atrapa el olor mientras el grumo permanece intacto, pero el amoníaco reaparece si la limpieza se retrasa; muchas marcas lo compensan con perfumes que irritan a gatos sensibles. El tofu controla bien los olores. Los pellets de madera neutralizan el amoníaco por la acción desodorante de la resina natural — sin enmascarar nada, el arenero simplemente huele a madera."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"salud-respiratoria"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Salud respiratoria"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Aquí la diferencia es categórica: la bentonita genera polvo de sílice que gato y familia respiran a diario. El tofu genera poco polvo; los pellets, ninguno. Para gatos con asma felina o alergias, la arena vegetal sin polvo es la recomendación estándar — lo explicamos a fondo en "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/blog/mejor-arena-para-gatos-con-alergias-o-problemas-respiratorios"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"nuestra guía para gatos con problemas respiratorios"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"economía-real"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Economía real"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"El precio por saco engaña; lo que importa es el costo por semana de uso. La bentonita se desecha en grumos que arrastran arena limpia. El tofu rinde de forma similar a la bentonita y su precio de importación es alto. Los pellets "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/blog/cuanto-dura-la-arena-de-pellets-para-gatos"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"rinden hasta 3 veces más"}]},{"type":"text","value":" porque solo se retira el material efectivamente usado: el costo semanal termina siendo el más bajo de los tres."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"impacto-ambiental"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Impacto ambiental"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"La bentonita se extrae de minas a cielo abierto, no se degrada y termina en rellenos sanitarios. El tofu es biodegradable, pero viaja miles de kilómetros hasta Ecuador. Los pellets de madera producidos localmente ganan en toda la línea: aprovechan residuos de la industria maderera (economía circular), son compostables en su propio jardín y su huella de transporte es mínima."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"veredicto"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Veredicto"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Para la mayoría de hogares ecuatorianos, la arena de pellets de madera ofrece el mejor balance: la más económica por semana de uso, la más saludable (cero polvo, cero químicos) y la única con producción nacional certificada. La bentonita conserva la ventaja de la costumbre, y el tofu es una alternativa vegetal digna aunque costosa."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Si decide probar los pellets, hágalo con método: la "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/blog/como-hacer-la-transicion-de-arena-tradicional-a-pellets"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"transición gradual en dos semanas"}]},{"type":"text","value":" garantiza que su gato acepte el cambio. Y si busca una opción hecha en Ecuador con madera de trazabilidad certificada, "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/#producto"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"conozca Popipet Ecoarena"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"los-tres-contendientes","depth":2,"text":"Los tres contendientes"},{"id":"comparativa-punto-por-punto","depth":2,"text":"Comparativa punto por punto"},{"id":"análisis-donde-cada-arena-gana-y-pierde","depth":2,"text":"Análisis: donde cada arena gana y pierde","children":[{"id":"control-de-olores","depth":3,"text":"Control de olores"},{"id":"salud-respiratoria","depth":3,"text":"Salud respiratoria"},{"id":"economía-real","depth":3,"text":"Economía real"},{"id":"impacto-ambiental","depth":3,"text":"Impacto ambiental"}]},{"id":"veredicto","depth":2,"text":"Veredicto"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:blog:arena-de-pellets-vs-arena-tradicional-vs-tofu.md","_source":"content","_file":"blog/arena-de-pellets-vs-arena-tradicional-vs-tofu.md","_stem":"blog/arena-de-pellets-vs-arena-tradicional-vs-tofu","_extension":"md"}